'''Afdhere Jama''' (dhashay [[1980]]) waa qoraa [[Soomaaliya|Soomaali]]-[[United States|Amerikaan]] ah oo ku saleysan magaalada [[San Francisco]]. Qoraalkiisa waxaa lagu arkaa daabacado ku yaal meelo badan oo aduunk ka mid ah. Wuxuu aasaasay ''[[Huriyah (magaaziin)]]'', magaaziin ka socda qajacyada Muslimminta ah. Ku dhashay kuna barbaarey Soomaaliya, Jama wuxuu yimid Markeykanka asagoo dhalinyaro ah. 

==Buugaagta==
* [[2004]] : ''Duhur la fariisadka Ilaahyada Soomaaliyeed'' (''At Noonday with the Gods of Somalia'', Salaam Press).
* [[2008]] : ''Dal'udhalasho Sharci La'aaneed: Qajacyada Dhulalka Muslimka'' (''Illegal Citizens: Queer Lives in the Muslim World'', Salaam Press).

